         Going to sneak this in here, otoh, my guildmate may become upset if his site gets 10230981908 hits.  </P><P>It all comes down to how you choose to weight different stats in this game on equipment.  As such, a guildmate has created a site, that has items updated from AK's pretty regularly, that allows you to put in your weighted values for just about everything, do a search, and see what the scores come out as.  It's a very nice tool, and in fact, my guildmate got mention in the Luclin manual for the site.</P><P>Website with the database.<BR><a href="http://www.squidbox.com/skp/eq/equipment/" target="_blank">http://www.squidbox.com/skp/eq/equipment/</a></P><P>Website to post updates to items, missing items, etc.. etc...<BR><a href="http://pub57.ezboard.com/fletalisericiusfrm8" target="_blank">http://pub57.ezboard.com/fletalisericiusfrm8</a></P><P>By the way, the current "default" values for the necromancer are NOT mine ;-)</P><P></P><P><BR>Kijam Orcen.<BR>Backwards Guhnome of E'ci<BR>Letalis Ericius<BR><a href="http://www.squidbox.com/skp/roster/roster.cgi?name=Kijam">Letalis Ericius Profile</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
